    Class Description
    Booking
    This class contains all information on the booking

    This class contains all information of the cinema

    This class contains information on the login service for admin
    Movie
    This class contains all information on a movie
    Review
    This class contains all information of a review - including the review's date, rating, review's content, reviewed Movie and name of reviewer
    Seat
    This class contains all information of a seat - including its row number, column number, Show and whether it is booked

    This class contains information on the seat mapping of each showtime
    Show
    This class contains information on a show of a movie
    TicketCostService
    This class contains information on the ticket cost service for calculation of ticket price
